Parliament, Tuesday, 9 July 2019 – The Portfolio Committee on Justice and Correctional Services will tomorrow receive a briefing from the South African Human Rights Commission on its Annual Performance Plan (APP) and budget. It will also be briefed by the Public Protector South Africa on its APP and budget.
	
	Details are as follows: 
	Date: Wednesday, 10 July 2019
	Time: 10 am
	Venue: Committee Room M454, Fourth Floor, Old Assembly Building
	
	ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES 
	
	For media enquiries or interviews, please contact the committee’s Media Officer:
	Name: Rajaa Azzakani (Ms)
	Tel: 021 403 8437
